			<h3>Micro-targeting.<br/>Massive scale.</h3>			
			<div class="col-left">				
				<p>
					Clearspring's AddThis is the largest content sharing platform on the web. Leveraging our patent-pending 
					data processing engine, we aggregate information from over 200MM unique US users 
					monthly. Using our dynamic segmentation technology, we categorize them into influence and intent-based 
					audience segments. Audiences are assembled for your campaign by combining hundreds of these segments 
					â¬that's micro-targeting at massive scale.
				</p>	
				<p>
					<strong>Intent-based segments:</strong> Find the people that want to find you. Reach users across all 
					stages of the purchase funnel: awareness, interest, consideration, and in-market. Campaigns using our 
					intent segments have seen 2X-10X lift.
				</p>		
				<p>
					<strong>Influence-based segments:</strong> Jump-start your viral campaign. Reach users that share to 
					Facebook, Twitter, and other social sites. On average, users that share using AddThis influence  
					another 4 friends and followers. Campaigns using our influencers have seen a 20-50% lift in sharing.
				</p>
			</div>			
